for a trip to Central America, although it rather sounds like metro
Atlanta. There's a difference between a tourist and a real
traveler, and I know which one I am. Show me your ruins. Where's
your best restaurant? Pulitzer winner Michael Skube's weekly
lifestyle commentary. (Skube, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED
6/22.
