<P>
   ........OOO................OOO.........
</P>
<P>
   ........OOOO...............OOO.........
</P>
<P>
   .........OOOO............OOOO..........
</P>
<P>
   ..........OOOO..........OOOO...........
</P>
<P>
   ............OOOOOOOOOOOOOO.............
</P>
<P>
   ...............OOOOOOOO................
</P>
<P>
   ..................OO...................
</P>
<P>
   ..................OO...................
