<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-23 13:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2345 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ONBUSINESS-COLUMN-BOS     06-23 0762
