getting into, they knew they weren't pleased with what their
children had.
 &HT;    Still, not everyone was converted. While Silberman liked it, his
wife Karen thought it sounded militaristic. ``I guess we're having
a disagreement,'' she said. And Sandra Oviedo has a son who's
