<P>
   WINE-TALK (Undated) _ There is every reason to assume that
California sangioveses will continue to improve. But except for the
few mentioned here, most are indifferent wines when compared to
other California and Tuscan red wines. Unless you are a California
fanatic, there is no reason to drink so-so sangioveses when there
are dozens of excellent little Chiantis out there for under $10. By
Frank J. Prial.
