<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-23 17:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2816 &Cx1f; ttx-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX     06-23 0365
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX </SLUG>
 
 
