<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    MICROSOFT WINS COURT VICTORY
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
