</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HAWKS-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Hawks have option after option for NBA draft
 &HT;    By Jeffrey Denberg
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
