<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-23 21:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3268 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-WORLDCUP-VI     06-23 0037
