   (NYT7) NEW YORK -- June 23, 1998 -- 14UP-FILM-REVIEW-1-B&AMP;W, 6-23
-- Phil Joanou filming the American version of ``7 Up'' in 1990;
7-year-old Luis, left, during the shoot. That demographically
correct band who became America's darlings in 1991 has returned in
a second installment of the documentary series that is following
